Name: Save The Girls

Pass 30 levels in the game, get stars, unlock different characters, and get in touch with them. A night of passion, enjoy unparalleled joy. Colorful stories Every beautiful girl will have her own exclusive plot, some are warm, some are touching, some are tragic, everything is up to you. Don't worry about missing any plot direction, you can change different options at will according to the plot chapters. Game Features Each beautiful girl has a complete Japanese dubbing. 6 characters dynamic CG 30 well-set levels one handed mode
